Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive
Epidemiological comments: the virus lineage of the 2 first outbreaks [in Mughar, 20180911.6021871 & in Shaal, 20180929.6060436] is O/ME/Panasia-2. The lineage of the other outbreaks is pending.

Control measures
